---
import { APP_CONFIG } from 'appConfig';
import { technologies, resumeURL } from './config';
---

<Fragment>
  <p>
    <span
      >Hey there&nbsp;👋🏻&nbsp;&nbsp;I’m Fateh, a Front-End engineer based in <span class="font-[500] text-text-bold"
        >Chennai, India</span
      >.</span
    >
  </p>
  <p>
    I’ve worked with <a href="https://www.thoughtworks.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Thoughtworks</a> previously
    and have
    <span class="font-[500] text-text-bold">4+ years</span> of experience developing complex, performant web apps with modern
    tools and technologies.
  </p>
  <p>
    Front-End is my passion! I get a kick out of exploring its ever-changing world since there is always something new
    to learn and experiment. I like to give users that first impression that makes them want to stay on the page.
  </p>
  <p>
    I’m a knowledge seeker and have an innately curious persona. I find building websites accessible by people around
    the world on a multitude of devices pretty amazing!
  </p>
  <p>
    <h5>Few technologies in my current stack:</h5>
    <div class="tech-item-grid">
      {
        technologies.map((item, index) => (
          <div class="tech-item" style={`animation-delay: ${index * 0.06}s`}>
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-primary mr-3" />
            <span>{item}</span>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </p>
  <p>
    My most recent obsession has been around dev tooling and bundlers, and I’m always open to chat about all things
    front-end, performance, and open source!
  </p>
  <p>
    I’m just off my personal break and <span class="font-[500] text-text-bold">currently open</span> to explore new opportunities.
  </p>
  <p>
    You can reach me at <a
      href={`mailto:${APP_CONFIG.USER.social.email}`}
      onclick="this.href=this.href.replace('@@','.')">fa7ehak[at]gmail<span class="hidden">@@</span>.com</a
    >
  </p>
  <p>
    <span>View my&nbsp;</span><a href={resumeURL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Résumé</a><i
      class="fas fa-arrow-up-right-from-square text-sm ml-1"></i>
  </p>
</Fragment>

<style>
  .tech-item-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;

    @media (max-width: theme('screens.lg.max')) {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    @media (max-width: theme('screens.md.max')) {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    @media (max-width: theme('screens.sm.max')) {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(1, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  .tech-item {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadein 0.4s ease forwards;

    & > i {
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    @media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine) {
      &:hover > i {
        transform: translateX(5px);
      }
    }
  }
</style>
